body_html: @Sanghoon94 Please open a different GitHub issue. Without code you are asking for a guess that will not end up being very useful. No guarantee someone will look at it but sharing the code allows for a better conversation. You might also want to upgrade to TF 1.2.1 or TF 1.3 just to be more current as if anyone on the team tests the example you provide, they are going to use a much newer binary. TF 1.0 is essentially 6 months old.
